I need to identify the line item that represents interest accrued but not yet received (interest receivable) and extract its initial and end values.

Looking at the balance sheet provided in the problem:

1. I can see the line item labeled "Interest Receivable" which represents interest that has been earned but not yet collected.

2. The initial value for Interest Receivable as of 2023-12-31 is 0.00

3. The end value for Interest Receivable as of 2024-02-01 is 6494.02

This is exactly what I'm looking for - interest that has accrued but hasn't been received yet.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '6494.02'}}
```
